data.description: Newly updated  tri-level home in central location! New paint & flooring throughout all levels of the home! Great curb appeal with large front yard, extended parking area, newer stucco exterior, and new windows. Inside, the main level features an open floor plan with sight lines to the eat-in kitchen. Updated cabinets, backsplash and counters with modern accents. Walk out to spacious, fully fenced backyard with convenient storage shed. Attached garage entrance off the kitchen as well. Upper level has 2 large bedrooms and a full bathroom. Lower level has the 3rd bedroom, half bathroom, spacious family room and laundry space. New roof in 2020. Brand new water heater Feb 2024. Conveniently located near I-25, schools, parks, military bases and shopping. This home has an assumable loan!
